Package com.smartsheet.api.internal.http

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HttpClient
    This interface defines methods to make an HTTP request.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidHttpClient  
    DefaultHttpClient
    This is the Apache HttpClient (http://hc.apache.org/httpcomponents-client-ga/index.html) based HttpClient implementation.
    HttpEntity
    This class represents an HTTP Entity (http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec7.html).
    HttpEntitySnapshot
    this extension of HttpEntity is only for the purpose of creating a copy of its data stream so that the original can be used as-received and this duplicate can be logged if needed
    HttpMessage
    This is the base class of HTTP messages, it holds headers and an HttpEntity.
    HttpRequest
    This class represents an HTTP request.
    HttpResponse
    This class represents an HTTP response.
    RequestAndResponseData
